USE hahn; $fullfilment_partners = (
    SELECT id
        FROM `/home/market/production/mbi/dictionaries/partner_biz_snapshot/latest`  with inline
        WHERE is_fullfilment = 1
);

$msku_with_fullfilment_supplier = (
    SELECT approved_market_sku_id as msku
    FROM `/home/market/production/ir/ultra-controller/supplier_to_market_sku`  with inline
    WHERE shop_id in $fullfilment_partners
);

$assortment = (
    SELECT
        model_id    AS msku,
        title,
        category_id,
        FROM `/home/market/production/mbo/export/recent/models/sku`  with inline
        WHERE model_id > 0 AND title != '' AND category_id > 0
        AND model_id IN $msku_with_fullfilment_supplier
);

SELECT
    a.msku                      AS msku,
    a.title                     AS title,
    a.category_id               AS category_id,
FROM $assortment AS a
